Privacy Policy

Last updated: March 01, 2025

Grater Games ("us", "we", or "our") developer of Gnome's Escape (the "App").

This page informs you of our policies regarding the collection,
use and disclosure of Personal Information we receive from users of the App.

By using the App, you agree to the collection and use of information in accordance with this policy.

Information Collection And Use
============================================
Gnome's Escape does not collect any personal information.
============================================
The App does store the high score localy on the device.
The App does read the high score stored localy on the device.



